name: 2021 5th International Conference on Intelligent Systems, Metaheuristics & Swarm Intelligence
content: For papers submitted to ISMSI 2021, we offer the publication as following: Accepted Papers after registration and presentation at ISMSI 2021 will be published inInternational Conference Proceedings, which will be indexed by Ei Compendex, Scopus, and submitted to be reviewed by Thomson Reuters (ISI Web of Science).
